---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - PetiKVX" 
  description="Privacy policy for PetiKVX's cybersecurity research website. Learn how we handle data and protect your privacy."
>
  <div class="relative min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/10 via-transparent to-blue-500/10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl shadow-green-500/30 animate-pulse">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 via-blue-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight font-mono">
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-mono">
            How we protect and handle your information
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4 font-mono">Last updated: November 2, 2025</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <section class="py-16 relative">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Introduction -->
          <div class="bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> Introduction</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-mono">
              This privacy policy describes how PetiKVX ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and protects 
              information when you visit our website. We are committed to protecting your privacy and maintaining 
              the security of any information we collect.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-mono">
              As a cybersecurity researcher, we take data protection seriously and follow industry best practices 
              to ensure your information remains secure.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Information Collection -->
          <div class="bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> Information We Collect</h2>
            
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-blue-400 font-mono">Automatically Collected Information</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-3 font-mono text-sm">
                When you visit our website, certain information is automatically collected, including:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-mono text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                  <span>Browser type and version</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                  <span>Operating system</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                  <span>IP address (anonymized)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                  <span>Pages visited and time spent on pages</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                  <span>Referring website</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-blue-400 font-mono">Information You Provide</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-mono text-sm">
                We may collect information you voluntarily provide when you:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-mono text-sm mt-3">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                  <span>Subscribe to our newsletter</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                  <span>Contact us through social media platforms</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                  <span>Interact with our GitHub repositories</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- How We Use Information -->
          <div class="bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-mono text-sm">
              We use the collected information for the following purposes:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 font-mono text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2 font-bold">1.</span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Website Analytics:</strong> To understand how visitors use our site and improve user experience</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2 font-bold">2.</span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Content Delivery:</strong> To provide you with relevant cybersecurity research and articles</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2 font-bold">3.</span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Security:</strong> To detect and prevent fraudulent or malicious activities</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2 font-bold">4.</span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Communication:</strong> To respond to inquiries and provide updates (with your consent)</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Third-Party Services -->
          <div class="bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-mono text-sm">
              This website is hosted on GitHub Pages and may use the following third-party services:
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-green-500/10">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-blue-400 font-mono">GitHub Pages</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm font-mono">
                  Our site is hosted on GitHub Pages. Please review 
                  <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-green-400 hover:text-green-300 underline">
                    GitHub's Privacy Policy
                  </a>
                  for information about their data practices.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-green-500/10">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-blue-400 font-mono">External Links</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm font-mono">
                  Our website contains links to external sites (GitHub, Twitter/X, etc.). We are not responsible 
                  for the privacy practices of these external sites.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Cookies -->
          <div class="bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> Cookies and Tracking</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-mono text-sm">
              Our website uses minimal cookies and tracking technologies:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-mono text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for basic site functionality</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Analytics:</strong> To understand site usage (anonymized)</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4 font-mono text-sm">
              You can control cookies through your browser settings. See our 
              <a href="/my-new-site/cookies/" class="text-green-400 hover:text-green-300 underline">Cookie Policy</a>
              for more details.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Data Security -->
          <div class="bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> Data Security</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-mono text-sm">
              We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-mono text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span>HTTPS encryption for all connections</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span>Regular security audits and updates</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span>Limited data collection and retention</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span>No storage of sensitive personal information</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Your Rights -->
          <div class="bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-mono text-sm">
              You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-mono text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Access:</strong> Request access to the information we have about you</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate information</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your information</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">></span>
                <span><strong class="text-green-400">Opt-out:</strong> Unsubscribe from communications at any time</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4 font-mono text-sm">
              To exercise these rights, please contact us through our 
              <a href="/my-new-site/contact/" class="text-green-400 hover:text-green-300 underline">contact page</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Updates -->
          <div class="bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> Policy Updates</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-mono text-sm">
              We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes 
              by posting the new policy on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. We encourage you to 
              review this policy periodically for any changes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500/10 to-blue-500/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-green-500/30 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-400 font-mono">> Questions or Concerns?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-mono text-sm">
              If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or our data practices, 
              please don't hesitate to reach out.
            </p>
            <a href="/my-new-site/contact/" 
               class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 text-black rounded-lg font-bold hover:from-green-400 hover:to-blue-400 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg shadow-green-500/30 font-mono">
              Contact Us
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
